<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.7.4">
<l>kāṇa vanteṉa kaṇmukappē tāmaraik kaṇpiṟaḻa</l>
<l>vāṇi cempoṉ mēṉiyentāy niṉṟaruḷā yeṉṟeṉṟu</l>
<l>nāṇa millāc ciṟutakaiyē ṉāṉiṅ kalaṟṟuvateṉ</l>
<l>pēṇi vāṉōr kāṇamāṭṭāp pīṭuṭai yappaṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Saying [and] saying “graciously stand, my father with the excellent red golden body,”</l>
<l>while the lotus eyes are twinkling at the front of the eye, because I have come to see</l>
<l>the father with a greatness that the celestials cannot esteem [and] see,</l>
<l>what of the prattle here of me who has little fitness without shame?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
